{"id":647954,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/06/魔都囡-我不会用智能手机，你们是不是准备让我/","date":"2020-06-22T20:32:39Z","modified":"2020-06-22T23:13:11Z","title":"魔都囡 | 我不会用智能手机，你们是不是准备让我去死？","content":"<p>哎……我们今天看到这个消息真的是整整难过了一天，其实这个事情我们早就想吐槽，这个社会有时候真的是太过分了。</p>\n<p>老实说，我们看到这个事情真的眼泪水都下来了。事情非常简单，6月17日，浙江台州，货车司机刘师傅，拉完货返程时，遇见一位大爷向他招手。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647955\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码1-1-300x241.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码1-1-300x241.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码1-1-768x616.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码1-1.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>老大爷问这位刘师傅，问他城里还有多远？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647956\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码2-300x164.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码2-300x164.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码2-768x421.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码2.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>实际上当时已经在半山腰了，可以想象老大爷走了多远，老大爷是安徽人，准备去黄岩投靠亲戚。可以看到，老大爷背着包带着锅碗瓢盆，非常凄惨。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647957\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码3-2-300x164.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码3-2-300x164.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码3-2-768x421.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码3-2.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是因为没有钱吗？这种情况虽然很惨，但是也不见得少见？不，说出原因可能大家都不信，大爷基本的生活开销还是有点的，但是他是硬生生的被逼着走了将近1000公里。</p>\n<p>我们测算了一下，亳州到黄岩的距离：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647958\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码4-1-300x195.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码4-1-300x195.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码4-1.png 573w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>开车的话差不多是950公里左右，徒步简直无法想象。老大爷就这么硬生生走了大半个月，真的是餐风露宿。可能你觉得奇怪，为何他其实有点钱却要被逼着走这将近数千公里？</p>\n<p>答案令人啼笑皆非：因为他没有手机！</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647959\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码5-1-200x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"749\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码5-1-200x300.png 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码5-1.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647960\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码6-1-300x69.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"115\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码6-1-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码6-1.png 711w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647961\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码7-1-300x66.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"109\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码7-1-300x66.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码7-1.png 705w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647962\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码8-300x60.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"99\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码8-300x60.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码8.png 719w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647963\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码9-300x63.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"105\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码9-300x63.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码9.png 692w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>我们简直要吐血！就因为一个健康码，活生生把一个几十岁的老人家逼得走路走了大半个月，几百公里的路程。叫做老人身体还算硬朗，万一走到一半劳累过度出点什么事情，这笔账算谁的？</p>\n<p>老人非常善良，刘师傅带着他走了很长一段，还带他去吃了面，老人家执意要还钱给刘师傅。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647964\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码10-300x166.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码10-300x166.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码10-768x424.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码10.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>老人家真的非常淳朴善良。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647965\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码11-228x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"658\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码11-228x300.png 228w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码11.png 713w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>大爷的亲戚在菜市场这里，菜市场晚上门锁了，没法进去。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647966\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码12-204x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"737\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码12-204x300.png 204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码12-695x1024.png 695w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码12.png 715w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>刘师傅人非常好，想让大爷到他那里住。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647967\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码13-250x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"601\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码13-250x300.png 250w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码13.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647968\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码14-300x46.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"77\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码14-300x46.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码14-768x119.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码14.png 910w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647969\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码15-300x56.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"93\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码15-300x56.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码15.png 717w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>大爷非常善良，不想再给刘师傅添麻烦，刘师傅心里非常难受。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647970\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码16-300x165.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码16-300x165.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码16-768x423.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码16.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最后刘师傅只能难过的离开，因为他知道，大爷没有健康码是没法乘坐任何公共交通工具的。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647971\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码17-300x165.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"275\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码17-300x165.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码17-768x422.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码17.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是大爷留给刘师傅的笑容。然后大爷转身去了公园露宿，可以想象，他那么多天都是这么过来的。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647972\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码18-203x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"738\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码18-203x300.png 203w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码18-694x1024.png 694w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码18.png 718w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>很显然，这个事情的问题显然就是出在这个手机上。</p>\n<p>我们对于健康码没有疑问，这是一个相对有效的防疫措施，但是这个措施在设计之初，有无考虑过那些没有手机的人？对于这部分人群，没有办法出示健康码是否有足够有效的措施帮助帮助他们？</p>\n<p>我们前几天在新华社的一篇文章中看到了这样一个惊人的数字：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647973\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码19-300x89.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"149\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码19-300x89.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码19-768x228.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码19.png 995w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>我们现在的中国，竟然有6亿人月可支配收入仅有1000元左右。</p>\n<p>这个不是危言耸听，这个是血淋淋的现实。这个是中国统计年鉴中的一段：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647974\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码20-300x80.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"133\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码20-300x80.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码20-1024x273.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码20-768x205.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码20.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>可以很简单的测算出来，占全国总人口四成份额的中等偏下收入群体与低收入群体，刚好处在“月收入1000元左右”这一区间内，再加上中等收入群体中一小部分收入较低的人口，规模恰恰就是差不多6亿。</p>\n<p>没有手机的人比我们想象的多得多！很多人一辈子就在简陋的老家深居简出，日出而作，日落而息，外面信息化高速发展和他们其实没太大关系。</p>\n<p>网友都怒了：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647975\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码21-300x68.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码21-300x68.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码21-768x175.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码21.png 875w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647976\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码22-300x68.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"113\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码22-300x68.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码22-768x174.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码22.png 880w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647977\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码23-300x54.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"90\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码23-300x54.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码23-768x138.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码23.png 871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647978\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码24-300x129.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"215\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码24-300x129.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码24-768x330.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码24.png 868w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647979\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码25-300x83.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"138\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码25-300x83.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码25-768x212.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码25.png 874w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647980\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码26-300x99.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"164\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码26-300x99.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码26-768x252.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码26.png 867w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>而事实上，这个甚至不是<strong>有无手机</strong>的问题，而是有无<strong>智能手机</strong>的问题！</p>\n<p>普通的打电话的老年机还不行！</p>\n<p>刚刚过去618，相信大家都在网上血拼的很猛吧，不知道大家有无换手机呢？华为？苹果？三星？大家可曾知道有这么一类手机是完全不具备上网等智能应用的，连个微信APP都没法装，只能打电话和发消息？</p>\n<p>这类手机一般统称为：老人机！</p>\n<p>我们随便截取个某东的老人机销量截图让大家看看，可能大家都不知道2020年了还有这种手机，注意销量：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647981\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码27-300x160.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码27-300x160.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码27-768x410.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码27.png 964w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647982\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码28-300x154.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"257\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码28-300x154.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码28-768x395.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码28.png 962w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>我们有点年纪的人都知道这种手机，很多人都是从这种手机到智能手机来了，很多年轻可能未必知道有这种手机，看看这个销量大家都应该明白，现在整个社会上有多少人在用这种非智能的老年机？</p>\n<p>对，老年机面对健康码这种依然无能为力。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647983\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码29-300x70.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"117\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码29-300x70.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码29-768x180.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码29.png 864w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647984\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码30-300x112.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"186\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码30-300x112.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码30-768x286.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码30.png 864w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647985\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码31-300x68.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"113\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码31-300x68.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码31-768x173.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码31.png 865w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>老年人限于知识文化和实际需求，只用老人机有错吗？有罪吗？很多老人究其一生恐怕都无法学会怎么去安装APP，怎么去微信和人家聊天，怎么去用小程序，怎么去扫二维码，怎么去关注公众号……那又如何？是老人的错吗？</p>\n<p>事实上，对于老人机无法用健康码，在过去的几个月里已经频繁出现，每个案例都让人非常难受，大多数人甚至不一定知道这些案例。</p>\n<p>3月份出的事情，黑龙江，五大连池，防疫人员要求老人扫码出示健康码，但是老人用的就是老人机，怎么扫码？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647986\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码32-300x236.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码32-300x236.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码32-768x603.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码32.png 926w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>老人急的双脚跳，“我的手机没法扫码你让我怎么扫？”这还有家不能回了？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647987\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码33-300x237.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码33-300x237.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码33-768x606.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码33.png 926w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>我们不能说防疫人员不负责任，在3月份这种时期，防疫人员的压力也很大，他不放老人过去。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647988\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码34-300x236.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"393\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码34-300x236.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码34-768x603.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码34.png 926w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最后甚至大打出手……</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647989\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码35-300x190.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"317\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码35-300x190.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码35-768x487.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码35.png 954w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>你很难想象现代的社会会有老人因为使用老人机最后被打伤住院……</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647990\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码36-300x199.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码36-300x199.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码36-768x511.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码36.png 925w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是最后的通报，防疫人员被处理：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647991\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码37-300x215.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"359\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码37-300x215.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码37.png 718w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>魔幻吗？还有呢，3月20日，镇江发生了几乎一模一样的事情。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647992\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码38-300x245.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"408\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码38-300x245.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码38.png 766w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>老人上公交车，结果呢？无法出示健康码，最后导致公交车迟迟不能发车，导致群众群起而攻之。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647993\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码39-218x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"688\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码39-218x300.png 218w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码39.png 432w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647994\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码40-300x65.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"108\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码40-300x65.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码40.png 439w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>甚至有人大声呵斥老人，你不下去就报警！</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647995\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码41-219x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"684\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码41-219x300.png 219w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码41.png 435w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647996\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码42-222x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码42-222x300.png 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码42.png 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>根据当时一位目击者的描述：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647997\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码43-300x149.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码43-300x149.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码43-768x381.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码43.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最终的原因是这位浦先生透露的，老人无法出示健康码的被围攻的原因赫然就是使用的是老人机，没有办法扫健康码。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647998\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码44-300x137.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"228\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码44-300x137.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码44-1024x466.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码44-768x350.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码44.png 1069w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>乘客们为了自己的时间，把这些使用老人机的老年人一个一个赶下车，我们看到实在是很难过很难过！</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-647999\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码45-300x136.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码45-300x136.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码45-1024x465.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码45-768x349.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码45.png 1062w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>其中一个老人，足足被人围攻骂了20多分钟，可怜的不得了，最终才有了这个曝光。根据统计，差不多有5~6个老人被赶下车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648000\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码46-300x136.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"227\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码46-300x136.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码46-768x349.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码46.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这个社会什么时候变成了老人因为使用老人机连公交车都无法乘坐了？根据当时的描述，其实很多老人还有社区开的纸条，但是依然无法乘坐公交车。网友都非常愤怒：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648001\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码47-300x69.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"115\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码47-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码47-768x177.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码47.png 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648002\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码48-300x133.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"221\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码48-300x133.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码48-768x339.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码48.png 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648003\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码49-300x69.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"115\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码49-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码49-768x177.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码49.png 847w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648004\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码50-300x85.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"142\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码50-300x85.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码50-768x218.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码50.png 860w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648005\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码51-300x114.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"190\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码51-300x114.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码51-768x292.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码51.png 857w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648006\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码52-300x146.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码52-300x146.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码52-768x374.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码52.png 859w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在过去几个月特殊时期，很多地方的公交车都要求实名登记，这是我们从某县发布这里摘录的乘坐公交的须知一部分：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648007\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53-300x181.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"301\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53-300x181.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53-768x463.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53-627x376.png 627w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53-440x264.png 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码53.png 851w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>看到没有？如果没有智能手机的完全无法搞定这些步骤。在过去的几个月，真正是没有健康码简直是寸步难行，进超市和商场要扫码。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648008\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码54-300x170.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"284\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码54-300x170.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码54-768x435.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码54.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>乘车要扫码：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648009\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码55-300x223.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"372\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码55-300x223.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码55-768x571.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码55.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>进任何地方都要扫码：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648010\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码56-300x247.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码56-300x247.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码56-768x632.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码56.png 1005w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在过去的几个月，经常出现的场景就是一群人围在一起拿出手机扫码扫码再扫码，如果一天去的地方多了，扫码几乎是不停顿……</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648011\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码57-300x225.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码57-300x225.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码57-768x576.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码57.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>有无考虑过那些用老人机的老人？</p>\n<p>这是实拍的某公交车上的二维码，完成这些步骤才能上车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648012\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码58-194x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"774\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码58-194x300.png 194w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码58-662x1024.png 662w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码58.png 729w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>我们不能说这些措施不对，对于大部分的现代人来说，似乎不是什么太大的问题，但是对于上述的那一部分不算少数的老年人来说，简直是要了命了。</p>\n<p>这是一位网友分享的一对父子乘坐公交车的经历，手机是智能机，有微信和支付宝，但是就是无法扫码：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648013\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码59-272x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"552\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码59-272x300.png 272w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码59-768x848.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码59.png 837w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>同样的，很多人都让这对父子下车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648014\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码60-300x168.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"280\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码60-300x168.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码60-768x430.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码60.png 828w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>作者比较好心，帮他手机试图注册搞一下，结果也卡主，他的支付宝账户不知道为何无法绑定：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648015\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码61-300x202.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码61-300x202.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码61-768x518.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码61.png 837w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最后这对父子还是下了车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648016\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码62-300x187.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码62-300x187.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码62-768x479.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码62-400x250.png 400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码62.png 822w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是网友分享的家里老人被智能手机卡在社会上的其他案例：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648017\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码63-300x146.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"243\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码63-300x146.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码63-768x374.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码63.png 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>不止是健康码，现在几乎到哪里都必须用手机。</p>\n<p>我们印象最深的是盒马刚刚出来的时候不收现金，只支持手机支付，搞的很多老人根本无法购物，引发很大争议，最后央妈出来表态：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648019\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码65-300x105.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"175\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码65-300x105.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码65-768x268.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码65.png 942w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>最终不得不搞了一个现金的通道：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648020\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码66-204x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"734\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码66-204x300.png 204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码66-698x1024.png 698w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码66.png 703w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>但是现在越来越多的地方只支持手机支付：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648021\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码67-300x147.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码67-300x147.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码67-768x376.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码67.png 862w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>不仅仅是支付，我们现在出去吃个饭，扫码点餐。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648022\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码68-300x225.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"374\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码68-300x225.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码68.png 533w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>很多饭店甚至已经取消了实体菜单，只能手机点餐。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648023\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码69-300x200.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码69-300x200.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码69-768x511.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码69.png 792w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是网友的实话：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648024\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码70-300x102.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"171\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码70-300x102.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码70-768x262.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码70.png 855w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>而最要命的是现在很多的医院也全面开始网上预约登记等，大部分都是在手机上操作。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648043\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/71-300x256.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"426\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/71-300x256.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/71-768x655.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/71.png 789w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是一位药师的感言：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648025\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码72-300x172.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码72-300x172.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码72.png 602w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这是网友的感受:</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648026\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码73-300x148.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"247\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码73-300x148.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码73-768x380.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码73.png 854w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648027\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码74-300x97.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"162\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码74-300x97.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码74-768x249.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码74.png 862w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648028\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码75-300x84.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"140\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码75-300x84.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码75-768x215.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码75.png 847w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648029\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码76-300x115.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"191\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码76-300x115.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码76-768x294.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码76.png 850w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>很多老人机之所以流行就是因为字大，而现在的那些网上先进的东西，字小得一点点，老人根本看不清楚。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648030\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码77-300x84.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"140\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码77-300x84.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码77-768x215.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码77.png 855w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648031\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码78-300x83.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"139\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码78-300x83.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码78-768x214.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码78.png 856w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648032\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码79-300x69.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"114\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码79-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码79-768x176.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码79.png 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648033\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码80-300x111.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"186\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码80-300x111.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码80-768x285.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码80.png 857w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648034\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码81-300x82.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"137\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码81-300x82.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码81-768x210.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码81.png 863w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648035\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码82-300x69.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"116\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码82-300x69.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码82-768x178.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码82.png 861w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648036\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码83-300x83.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"138\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码83-300x83.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码83-768x212.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码83.png 855w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>前阶段，甚至著名的农民明星，我们写过的大衣哥朱之文去参观阿里也被手机阻拦在阿里门外。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648037\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码84-221x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"680\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码84-221x300.png 221w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码84.png 735w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>幸亏现场有很多年轻人帮忙解决了问题，可以想象，大衣哥尚且如此，还有多少农民、老人无法使用智能手机？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648038\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码85-270x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"556\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码85-270x300.png 270w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码85.png 736w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>2019年，我国60岁以上人口达到2.54亿，而截止到2018年9月，微信55岁至70岁用户有6100万人。巨大数量的老年人在哪？他们因为不会使用智能手机，被这个号称越来越便捷的世界抛在了背后。</p>\n<p>现在手机和网上业务的迅猛发展更是让很多老人连门都出不了，想去哪里兜兜，不好意思，要先预约，现在基本上最常见的3个操作：</p>\n<p>1、要么下载app；</p>\n<p>2、要么关注公众号；</p>\n<p>3、要么使用小程序。</p>\n<p>试问，对于很多老人而言，这些操作比登天还难，岁数和文化都已经不允许他们去掌握这些现代化的东西，难道就无路可走了？</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648039\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码86-300x219.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"366\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码86-300x219.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码86-768x561.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码86.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>现在几乎动不动就要关注公众号，动不动就要下载app已经变成了常态，对于很多老人而言，则是噩梦。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648041\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码88-300x115.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"192\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码88-300x115.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码88-768x295.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码88.png 853w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648042\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码87-300x145.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"242\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码87-300x145.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码87-768x371.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码87.png 857w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>其实这个手机的问题背后可以关联到很多很深的问题：</p>\n<p>1、这个社会是否对弱势群体友好？</p>\n<p>虽然部分群体都使用了智能手机，但是相当多的人还是没法使用，难道为了部分群体的利益可以无视这部分群体的利益？比如我们大多数都是健康人，是否可以取消少数盲人使用的盲道？显然不可以。</p>\n<p>2、是否有权力剥夺一部分人的生活选择权？</p>\n<p>都说科技以人为本，但是显然整个社会发展到现在，你说资本也好，其他的东西也好都在用权力去“逼你”这么做，逼你关注公众号，逼你下载app，逼你用小程序，逼你这个逼你那个，很多东西年轻人一时间都很难上手，都会搞的晕头转向，更别提那些老人，这些“权力”其实在毫无节制的剥夺了弱势群体的生活选择权。</p>\n<p>可能很多年轻人未必对这个话题感兴趣，但是请大家明白一个道理，我们都会老，年纪大了，学习的能力，认知的能力，各种兴趣都会下降明显（不开玩笑，我们已经感觉到了，对于新生事物，我们这一代已经远不如年轻人热衷了）。当我们老的时候，可能某天，一个我们从没看到过的新科技出现在我们面前，当年轻人指尖飞舞的快速操作，我们在旁边一筹莫展的时候，我们会是什么心情？</p>\n<p>科技发展是好事，社会信息化进步也是好事，但是请别忘了在很多地方，砸很多角落里，还有很多跟不上的人群，不该抛下他们，更不该遗忘他们的存在！</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-648040\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码89-300x130.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"217\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码89-300x130.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码89-768x333.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/06/扫码89.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>生活中不该都是扫码，不是每做一件事情都要把手机掏出来！</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38912,39924],"tags":[40184,40771,28701,33617,38834,34391]}